latestPosts.caption:
Wandered through one of the oldest markets in the Middle East — Khan el-Khalili in Cairo🤗

Dating back to the 14th century, this souq is a wild maze of antiques, spices, jewelry, vintage gems, and chaotic charm.

Tip: Take a breather at one of the cafés when the hustle gets too real🫢

A must-visit if Cairo’s on your list!
